      "message": "It might be useful to print a human-friendly error message here, the right way to do it is:\n\n  char *pstr \u003d NULL;\n  FormatMessage(FORMAT_MESSAGE_FROM_SYSTEM |\n                FORMAT_MESSAGE_ALLOCATE_BUFFER,\n                NULL,\n                GetLastError(),\n                0,\n                (LPTSTR)\u0026pstr,\n                2,\n                NULL);\n  // print error message with |pstr| here.\n  LocalFree(pstr);\n\nSadly, qemu doesn\u0027t provide a helper function to do that, and reimplements it throughout its source code base.",
